Sure, hit the mic.

680
00:48:13,938 --> 00:48:15,139
Awesome talk, thank you.

681
00:48:15,239 --> 00:48:15,759
That was great.

682
00:48:15,779 --> 00:48:16,179
Thanks.

683
00:48:17,340 --> 00:48:20,321
I just, I wanted to know what your opinion is on,

684
00:48:20,822 --> 00:48:23,323
I'm new to gaming and a lot of what I've encountered

685
